author: Duncan Lindsay
title: EastEnders spoilers: Will Nancy Carter die as Danny Dyer’s exit storyline as Mick is revealed?
text:
(Picture: BBC) Mick Carter has been left fearing the worst after receiving the news that his daughter Nancy has been hit by a car and is in a critical condition in EastEnders. Demanding the quickest plane ticket to Bulgaria, Mick used Ollie’s baby fund to pay to go and see Nancy. 
The sudden turn of events paves the way for Danny Dyer’s break from the role of Mick as he took a few weeks off from the show recently. A few weeks back, he was already in talks with EastEnders bosses about returning as his time off is just a short departure.
(Picture: BBC) But Nancy’s fate remains up in the air – are the Carters set to be hit by a whole new nightmare after everything they have endured recently?
(Picture: BBC) And can Whitney and Johnny hold everything together in Mick’s absence?
